OL,3,CGrieving family sent body of man, 77,
OL,4,Cinstead of their son who died abroad
OL,6,FThe grieving family of a young man
OL,7,Ffrom Nottingham who died abroad say
OL,8,Fthey have mistakenly been sent the
OL,9,Fbody of a 77-year-old man.
OL,11,FKevin Nightingale who was 39, died in
OL,12,FMay while he was working as a teacher
OL,13,Fin Cambodia.
OL,15,FHe had been living and teaching in the
OL,16,FTakeo province for around ten years.
OL,18,FHis family say they were were told by
OL,19,Fauthorities there he died from a heart
OL,20,Fattack.
