OL,3,CGrieving family sent body of man, 77,
OL,4,Cinstead of their son who died abroad
OL,6,FBut when they arrived at the funeral
OL,7,Fdirector after repatriation, his
OL,8,Fparents, Maureen Thompson and Stephen
OL,9,FNightingale, realised it was the body
OL,10,Fof the wrong man - a 77 year old
OL,11,FCanadian, and not their son.
OL,13,FMaureen and Stephen say the last two
OL,14,Fmonths have been like "living in a
OL,15,Fhorror movie", saying it has
OL,16,F"prolonged our heartache and worry".
OL,18,FMaureen says "He loved his job, he
OL,19,Fwent there and loved his life. All the
OL,20,Fkids called him the handsome teacher.
OL,21,FHe had his whole life ahead of him."
