OL,3,CGrieving family sent body of man, 77,
OL,4,Cinstead of their son who died abroad
OL,6,FKevin was found dead at his home by a
OL,7,Fcolleague on 3rd May, after not
OL,8,Fshowing up at work for two days.
OL,10,FAuthorities in Cambodia informed his
OL,11,Ffamily he had died after falling down
OL,12,Fthe stairs while having a heart attack.
OL,14,FMaureen says "I can't believe he just
OL,15,Fpassed away. You don't expect your own
OL,16,Fkids to pass before you".
OL,18,F"The shock and horror"
OL,20,FKevin's family say they had to raise
OL,21,F#7,500 to bring him home.
