OL,3,CGrieving family sent body of man, 77,
OL,4,Cinstead of their son who died abroad
OL,6,FEvergreen Funeral Services was
OL,7,Fresponsible for the repatriation.
OL,9,FBut the Cambodian repatriation service
OL,10,Freportedly sent the wrong body to
OL,11,FNottingham-based funeral director L.J.
OL,12,FCrawley on the 11th June.
OL,14,FMaureen went with Kevin's brother,
OL,15,FSean, to view who she thought would be
OL,16,Fher son, only to find the body of a
OL,17,Fman almost double his age.
OL,19,FShe said "I thought 'my God'. The
OL,20,Fshock and horror. We couldn't believe
OL,21,Fwhat our eyes were seeing.
