OL,3,CGrieving family sent body of man, 77,
OL,4,Cinstead of their son who died abroad
OL,6,F"Our minds were everywhere, it was
OL,7,Fpure panic stations, it was absolutely
OL,8,Fhorrendous."
OL,10,FStephen said "I felt sick to my
OL,11,Fstomach. Everyone's thoughts went to
OL,12,F'I hope they've not cremated him'."
OL,14,FBy the time Kevin's body arrived in
OL,15,Fthe UK it was so badly decomposed they
OL,16,Fsay he was "almost unrecognisable".
OL,18,FKevin's family were refunded the
OL,19,Frepatriation cost by Evergreen, but
OL,20,Fthey've described the mix-up as an
OL,21,F"absolute nightmare".
