OL,3,CGrieving family sent body of man, 77,
OL,4,Cinstead of their son who died abroad
OL,6,FThe Foreign Office confirmed it had
OL,7,Fassisted the family of a British man
OL,8,Fwho had died in Cambodia.
OL,10,F"How the hell did they get it mixed
OL,11,Fup?"
OL,13,FMaureen is calling for accountability,
OL,14,Fsaying "Someone has got to be held
OL,15,Faccountable for this because it made
OL,16,Fit all worse. It prolonged our
OL,17,Fheartache and worry.
OL,19,F"How the hell did they get it mixed
OL,20,Fup? It beggars belief. I've never
OL,21,Fknown anything like it in my life."
