OL,3,CGrieving family sent body of man, 77,
OL,4,Cinstead of their son who died abroad
OL,6,FStephen said "We just want someone to
OL,7,Fhold the can for this. The mistakes
OL,8,Fmade over there must have been
OL,9,Fhorrendous to confuse a 39-year-old
OL,10,Fwith a guy over 70. It's
OL,11,Fincomprehensible".
OL,13,FHe says "Surely there's custom checks
OL,14,Fand double-checks and triple-checks
OL,15,Fthey have to do?"
OL,17,FKevin's family are still awaiting the
OL,18,Fresults of swabs taken during a post-
OL,19,Fmortem in the UK, which they were told
OL,20,Fcould take 18 weeks.
