OL,6,FStephen paid tribute to his son,
OL,7,Fsaying "He was one of the nicest
OL,8,Fpeople you could meet. He was a
OL,9,Fheartbreaker and had a heart of gold."
OL,11,FEvergreen Funeral Services, which was
OL,12,Fresponsible for the repatriation, has
OL,13,Fnot responded to a request for comment.
